-- Qualcomm says Upaid Systems drops patent suits
-- 
-- Mon Apr 9, 2007 7:47am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/04/09/us-qualcomm-upaid-idUSWEN621820070409

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Upaid Systems Ltd. has agreed to drop all patent claims against Qualcomm Inc. ( QCOM.O ) over pre-paid and pre-authorized communication services and transactions, Qualcomm said on Monday. 

 The companies decided to settle the litigation, it said. Under the settlement, Qualcomm will receive a royalty-free worldwide license to the patents in the suit and any related patents.